data.description: STUNNING 2015 4 BR/3.5 BTH home w/ Navy FCU 3.5% ASSUMABLE VA loan for qualified veterans on quiet cul-de-sac features stone & siding, faces east and receives very good sunlight. Over 3600 SF finished space (4400+ SF total) combines  elegance, smart updates, excellent maintenance and superb location. From the sidewalk, note the golf course quality lawn, an example of the attention to detail in the care given to this home by the  owners, aided by the multi-zone Rainbird smart  sprinkler system. Also note the brand NEW 50-year architectural shingle roof (OCT 23).  Additionally, the exterior and interior of the home have been repainted including the exterior skirt, entry steps, porch, colums, rear walk-out stairs, etc. (OCT 2023) The front lawn exterior light top fixture was replaced. (SEP 2023) As you approach the entry door, you find the doorbell which is part of the new VIVINT security system containing multiple cameras and multiple additional sensors installed in AUG 2023. Once inside, you will quickly notice that the whole house interior has been repainted with Sherman Williams paint in Oct 2023. Additionally, the two-level entry foyer and stairs showcase hardwood and wrought iron ballasts which lead to new hardwood in the upper hallway (OCT 2023). The main level includes a formal living room, dining room, a gourmet kitchen which opens to an adjacent breakfast area, large family room and a nearby laundry/mud room. The gourmet kitchen features 42 inch cabinets, granite counters, a center island, desk, ceramic tile floors, and stainless steel appliances including a SS double wall oven, SS refrigerator, built-in SS microwave replaced SEP 2023, new gas cooktop (Summer 2023), and SS dishwasher. GE brand appliances are under warranty until FEB 2026. Notice the coffered ceiling, crown moulding and chair rail in the dining room (DR) and the crown moulding in the living (LR). Main level carpets have been stretched and cleaned. (OCT 2023) From the Breakfast Room take the freshly re-stained wood steps to the rear yard and patio. Upon stepping back inside, you find the new VIVINT security system (AUG 23) control panel near the main entry door.  Nearby the Laundry/Mud Room is next to the Family Room and includes a full size top load washer with a front loading dryer. The two-car garage is next to the laundry room. From the main level take the wooden stairs up to the sleeping level where all four (4)  bedrooms have NEW carpet (SEP 23). The spacious owner's suite includes two walk-in closets, coffered ceiling with crown moulding, ceiling fan w/ light, and a grand bath with a double vanity with granite counters, a soaking tub, separate shower, water closet, and linen closet. Three additional spacious bedrooms on this level all have new carpet and paint and share a bath. The basement includes a spacious Den, third full bath including tub with shower, plentiful storage area which could be converted to additional rooms, a utility room, and walk-out stairs. The deluxe 8X10 storage shed in the back yard conveys as well as the freshly washed wooden fence increases privacy.
